But I want to point out that prejudice against them might not just be bigotry, but the result of evolutionary phenomena explained through game theory.
The nomadic tribe that is gone next week has clear incentive to try and exploit the people they come into contact with, they have no incentive to "clean up" after themselves. This in return means that in order to protect their own group the local tribe has to treat them differently than they would their own.
